1.title: Sin cielo
1.plot: It's been three months since Cielo's disappearance.. Nico and Lleca look for Malvina and Cristobal in the jungle. Mar, Jazmin, Rama, Thiago and Tacho are at Rockland's summer camp. The Hogar Magico is being rebuilt. The CC (Cruz Corporation) switches Feli and Tina and is spying on the Teen Angels. Cielo makes an appearance.

2.title: No te rindas
2.plot: The teens escape the camp to go to a party, where Jaz flirts with Matt. Meanwhile, Lleca disappears in the jungle and Nico communicates with Cristobal. Mar and Thiago find a mysterious box.

3.title: Esperanza
3.plot: Mar meets Simón through a series of misunderstandings. Nico runs into his best friend, Salvador. Esperanza is born.

4.title: Cenicienta
4.plot: Alelí reads Cinderella. Cielo finds out Feli is Tina. Nacho, Tefi and their squad mess with the Teen Angels. Lleca mysteriously reappears.

5.title: Queridos reyes magos
5.plot: Nico, Malvina, Cristobal and Lleca leave the jungle. Nico has a dream in which Cielo appears. Rama, Nacho and Jero go to a party and things go south. Simón and Mar get closer. CC is implanting the kids. Cielo leaves to Eudamón.

6.title: El rulo vuelve
6.plot: Eudamón rejects Cielo since she is not ready. Rama faces the consequences after the crash. CC implants Mar and Rama and tries to kidnap Monito.

7.title: El elefantito rosa
7.plot: The Teen Angels get revenge from the "chetos". The mysterious golden box appears again. Tic-Tac teaches Cielo how to forget, but he is the one who ends up learning. Nico runs into Luca, a boy with secret intentions.

8.title: Bajo 7 llaves
8.plot: The book has 7 locks, no keys. The Teen arrive at the Hogar Mágico on it's opening day. Luca goes to the Hogar, he is a CC infiltrate. Cielo communicates with Nico.

9.title: Dejalo ser
9.plot: The girls meet Luca and he makes quite an impression. Rama tells Nico that he got expelled. Cielo interferes by telling Nico that Feli is actually Tina and Tic-Tac teaches her a lesson. Nico meets his new neighbor, Franka. Tacho gets kidnapped. Thiago runs into an old lover.

10.title: Vamos juntos
10.plot: Things go wrong when CC tries to implant Tacho. Rama gets re-accepted into the Rockland. Cielo is dying of sadness until she sings and dances with Nico and the kids. She manages to bring Nico where she is.

11.title: Tus deseos son órdenes
11.plot: Mar sees Thiago and Melody together. Cielo has to let Nico go. Rama meets a tough girl and helps her escape from the police. They get into trouble when she makes a car explode. Tacho starts fighting as the "Angel Rojo."

12.title: Retratos de familia
12.plot: Cielo, with Tac-Tic's help, sends signals to the kids. It's first day of school and the house is a chaos. Malvina hangs a picture of Cielo to make everyone feel better. Nico gets mad and tells the teens off. One of Cielo's signal leaves everyone astonished.

13.title: Hasta el santo desconfía
13.plot: Nico has a new lead on CC and when he follows it, he runs into someone he already knows.

14.title: El primer beso
14.plot: Simón realizes that "Tefi" is actually Mar. Cielo, devastated at the loss of her memories, attempts to have one last moment with Nico.

15.title: Tenés un mensaje nuevo
15.plot: Luca follows Tacho and finds out what he does at night. Cielo has to find the messenger. On her way to do it, she runs into unexpected person. A box is delivered to the Hogar Mágico for Cielo. Melody has a hidden agenda.

16.title: El amigo invisible
16.plot: Everyone plays "The Invisible friend". Franka tries to make Nico fall for her. A new girl comes to the Hogar, Caridad. Tic-Tac sends the keys to open the book, but there is a catch: they have to find them. Cielo returns from Eudamón.

17.title: Sigue al conejo blanco
17.plot: Vale and Rama mess things up. Everyone meets Caridad. Cielo says goodbye to Nico.

18.title: Encuentros
18.plot: Cielos escapes from CC and meets Salvador. Matt comes back. Nico visits Salvador.

19.title: Bautismos
19.plot: Nico messages Cielo without knowing it's actually her. The guys make a bet and someone gets hurt. Cielo sees Nico and the rest of the kids.

20.title: En el nombre del padre
20.plot: Hope get baptized. Franka catches Cielo. The Teen show Nico the book. Mar and Simón go boxing. Alelí sees Tina doing something bad. Cielo speaks on the phone with Nico.

21.title: El sentido de la vida
21.plot: Cielo goes to the Hogar but she isn't seen by anybody and, when she touches the book, something unexpected happens. Thiago makes a decision about the contest. Nico and Franka get closer.
